          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Too many products are built for shelf life, not skin. We believe healing should<br/>be both effective and kind-safe for your skin, your family, and the planet.</p><p><br/>The future of healing is clean-rooted in nature, backed by science, and free<br/>from compromise. It should work fast, feel good, and be trusted to care for<br/>your body as gently as it does powerfully.</p><p><br/>That's why we created First Honey: a new kind of care, made with medical-<br/>grade Mānuka honey from New Zealand and backed by serious science.<br/><br/></p>"
