        "text_7LNJ7A": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Mānuka honey is one of nature's most powerful healers. Rich in over 2,000 natural bioactive compounds-including methylglyoxal (MGO), a potent antibacterial agent-it helps repair skin, reduce inflammation, and accelerate healing.</p><p>Our proprietary medical-grade process turns this natural wonder into a clean, effective solution for:</p><ul><li>Cuts, scrapes, and burns.</li><li>Wound healing and post-op recovery.</li><li>Immune and digestive support.</li><li>Sensitive skin and everyday irritation.</li></ul><p>It's not just honey. It's healing that works.<br/><br/></p>",
